title: Clarification: Efficacy rates
text:
The Sputnik V Covid-19 vaccine's general efficacy of 92 per cent compares with 66.9 per cent overall efficacy of the Johnson & Johnson vaccine. An article on February 26 compared the Sputnik V general efficacy level with J&J rates of efficacy in preventing severe or critical disease of more than 80 per cent.
